	<p class="ArticleContent" align="center"><font style="color:#000080;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">Projects for Juche-oriented Industry Actively Pushed Ahead with</font></p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nbsp;</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Officials and working people of metallurgical and chemical industry push ahead with projects for Juche-oriented industry to carry out the important tasks set forth at the 4th Plenary Meeting of the 8th Central Committee of the Workers&rsquo; Party of Korea.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">The officials of the Ministry of Metal Industry actively strive to solve the problems arising in building structures, making accessories and assembling the equipment at the construction sites.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">The officials and working people of the Kim Chaek Iron and Steel Complex step up the construction of energy-saving oxygen-blast furnace and improve the capacity of producing oxygen.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Those of the Hwanghae Iron and Steel Complex accelerate the construction of energy-saving oxygen-blast furnace in real earnest.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">In the Chollima Steel Complex, the officials and working people level the ground for installing more curved type strand-casting machines and concentrate all the efforts on maintaining and reinforcing production process after scrupulously making daily plans.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Those of the chemical industry also strive to make the industry Juche-oriented.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Officials of the Ministry of Chemical Industry make detailed plans and meticulously organize all the work under the scientific and technological guarantee at the construction sites for developing Juche-oriented industry.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Meanwhile they take measures in advance for supplying materials in liaison with relevant institutions.</p><p class="ArticleContent" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Officials of different units including the Hungnam Fertilizer Complex and the Namhung Youth Chemical Complex scrupulously organize the work and arouse the creative enthusiasm of working people and technicians for solving technical problems.</p><p class="ArticleContent" align="right">Rodong Sinmun</p>	</td>
